attributes.title: Green Sound Panel
attributes.description:
Created on February 24, 2010 by isaacdvanwesep on Sourcemap.org:

A sound-absorbing panel with a 1-3 inch by several foot pad, and a cabinet or frame made from reclaimed or recycled board.  May include a badge of recycled glass & gold leaf.  Also has fittings for hanging to a wall
